title: 12/27: Start or Sit (AFC); Interesting Rankings (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Some of the more intriguing rankings in Week 17 involve Melvin Gordon, Russell Wilson, RBs in general and Deshaun Watson. We start the show discussing those guys ... News and notes from around the NFL (7:50) including a look at the complicated PIT and KC backfields ... NYJ-NE (10:30), CIN-PIT (18:45), CLE-BAL (25:25), IND-TEN (29:40), LAC-DEN (35:40), JAC-HOU (40:00), OAK-KC (44:25), MIA-BUF (50:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
